    ],
    "fonts": [
      "Times",
      "Times,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      7.0,
      10.0
    ],
    "text": "2. The following new section is hereby insertedimmediately after section 4 of the Recovery of Loans byBanks (Special Provisions) Act, No. 4 of 1990 and shallhave effect as section 4A of that Act:-"
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
